<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Login Notification</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>New Login Notification</h2>
    <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
    <p>We noticed a new login to your account from a new device.</p>
    <p>
      If this was you, you can ignore this email. Otherwise, please take action immediately by
      contacting us.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you didn't perform this action, we recommend changing your password and reviewing your
      account security settings.
    </p>
    <p>Device Information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Device Type:</strong> <%= device.type %></li>
      <li><strong>Device Name:</strong> <%= device.name %></li>
      <li><strong>Location:</strong> <%= device.location %></li>
      <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> <%= device.ip %></li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to contact us.</p>
    <p>Regards,</p>
    <p>CozyTrip</p>
  </body>
</html>
